addr="jms-011P"
type="local">Forester 5.0 [TBA]</fr:link> › new datalog-based query engine</fr:title></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>As the query engine has evolved, it has become a bit unwieldy and misshapen. In order to prevent further churn and facilitate the long-term development and use of <fr:link
href="jms-005P.xml"
title="Forester"
addr="jms-005P"
type="local">Forester</fr:link>, we are replacing the query engine and graph analysis with a more general tool: <fr:em>datalog</fr:em>. With this change comes the ability to introduce arbitrary relations of any arity; this is a powerful and dangerous tool, so use it wisely.</fr:p><fr:tree
show-metadata="false"><fr:frontmatter><fr:authors><fr:author><fr:link
href="jonmsterling.xml"
